729194f-a.title: Richmond: New Dorp Lane - 8th Street
729194f-a.text:
New Dorp Lane (right), south side, west from 9th Street
(foreground). The house, seen prominently, is a police station,
at the S.E. corner of 8th Street.
April 22, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
